@startuml seq-code-run
hide footbox
scale max 1500 width
scale max 2000 height
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
title 代码在线运行（异步全链路）

actor "登录用户" as Client
participant "RunController" as Ctl
participant "CodeRunService" as RunSvc
queue "RabbitMQ" as MQ
participant "RunRequestListener" as RunReq
participant "Envoy 运行服务" as Envoy
participant "RunResultListener" as RunRes
participant "CodeRunWebSocketHandler" as WS

note over Client, Ctl : JWT 鉴权；与判题链路独立

== 提交运行（同步） ==

Client -> WS : WebSocket 连接 /ws/run/{runId}
Client -> Ctl : POST /api/run\n(code, language, stdin, runId?)

Ctl -> RunSvc : enqueue(CodeRunRequest)
RunSvc -> RunSvc : 生成或校验 runId
RunSvc -> MQ : CodeRunQueueMessage
RunSvc --> Ctl : CodeRunAcceptedResponse(runId)
Ctl --> Client : 200 返回 runId

== 执行阶段（异步） ==

MQ -> RunReq : 消费运行请求
RunReq -> Envoy : POST /run
Envoy --> RunReq : CodeRunResponse

alt HTTP 或执行失败
  RunReq -> MQ : CodeRunQueueResult(error)
else 成功
  RunReq -> MQ : CodeRunQueueResult(response)
end

MQ -> RunRes : 消费运行结果
RunRes -> WS : pushRunResult(runId, message)
WS --> Client : WebSocket 推送 stdout / stderr

@enduml
